{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Theater of Life: Panggung Sandiwara yang Melebur Dalam Kenyataan","content":"\n<p>Kamu pasti tahu dong lagu Panggung Sandiwara? Lagu dari Ahmad Albar yang populer oleh Nicky Astria ini menceritakan bagaimana orang-orang “bersandiwara” di hidup mereka. Pesan yang sama bisa jadi dapat ditemukan di komik terbaru CIAYO Comics, Theater of Life.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53458\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/attachment/01-theatre-of-life/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-theatre-of-life\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life.jpg\" alt=\"Kemunculan Ryan membawa angin segar. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53458\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Kemunculan Ryan membawa angin segar. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ryan baru saja pindah ke sekolah barunya. Cowok blasteran\nini dengan cepat menarik perhatian murid-murid populer, sebut saja salah satunya\nIndah. Indah yang bisa dikatakan queen bee di kelasnya ini dengan jelas\nmenampilkan rasa tertariknya pada Ryan. Namun perhatian Ryan justru jatuh\nkepada Novi, siswi cuek bebek yang hanya dekat dengan teman sebangkunya Andre.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53459\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/attachment/02-theatre-of-life/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-theatre-of-life\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life.jpg\" alt=\"Novi dan Andre tak terpisahkan sejak kecil. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53459\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Novi dan Andre tak terpisahkan sejak kecil. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meskipun teman-teman lain mengatakan Novi dan Andre anak\nkuper dan bau rokok, tapi Ryan menemukan keanggunan dalam diri Novi yang sebodo\namat dengan hingar bingar sekolah. Kekaguman Ryan bertambah setelah mengikuti\nklub teater, dimana ia menyaksikan penampilan Novi yang penuh emosi dan totalitas.\nRyan makin tertantang untuk bisa kenalan dengan Novi, namun merasa canggung\nkarena ada Andre di dekatnya. Apalagi Ryan juga nggak bisa leluasa karena\nditempeli Indah. Apakah Ryan bisa menguak sosok asli Novi yang tersembunyi di\nbalik topeng kecuekannya?</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53460\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/attachment/03-theatre-of-life/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-theatre-of-life\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life.jpg\" alt=\"Indah, karakter yang (jelas-jelas) antagonis dalam Theater of Life. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53460\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Indah, karakter yang (jelas-jelas) antagonis dalam Theater of Life. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Theater of Life merupakan satu lagi judul komik yang dikerjakan <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/12pulang\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Studio 12pulang (opens in a new tab)\">Studio 12pulang</a>. Dengan cerita dan storyboard rancangan riameco, Juan Farrel dan FairyDemon; serta ilustrasi dari Vivi Len, komik ini menitik beratkan hubungan pertemanan dan romansa yang rumit dari berbagai karakter. Baik sosok Ryan, Novi, Indah dan Andre saling terhubung dengan dinamikanya yang menarik.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53461\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/attachment/04-theatre-of-life/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-theatre-of-life\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life.jpg\" alt=\"Novi menampilkan sisi lainnya di atas panggung. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53461\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Novi menampilkan sisi lainnya di atas panggung. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tentu semua itu bakal sia-sia kalau nggak didukung dengan\npenokohan yang juga sama menariknya, kan? Lihat aja Novi, sang main heroine\nyang ternyata bukan tipe damsel in distress yang cuma bisa nangis. Sosoknya\ncuek bebek, dan bisa blak-blakan kalau diserang duluan. Tapi kalau sudah\nberakting, sosoknya berubah 180 derajat!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53462\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/theater-of-life-panggung-sandiwara-yang-melebur-dalam-kenyataan/attachment/05-theatre-of-life/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-theatre-of-life\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life.jpg\" alt=\"Apakah Novi dan Andre berpacaran? Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53462\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/05-theatre-of-life-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Apakah Novi dan Andre berpacaran? Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kalau kamu penasaran dengan kelanjutan kisah Theater of Life, ikutin aja serial komiknya setiap hari Minggu pukul 20:00 WIB, hanya di CIAYO Comics. Eh tapi tunggu dulu! Kenapa cuma ada 3 episode aja? Jangan panik, karena kelanjutannya bisa kamu dapatkan di <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/segera-update-ciayo-comics-plus/\" target=\"_blank\">CIAYO Comics Plus</a>. Hanya dengan 15 ribu Rupiah per bulannya, kamu bisa membaca berbagai <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/8-komik-eksklusif-ciayo-comics-plus-yang-harus-kamu-ikutin/\" target=\"_blank\">komik eksklusif</a>, baca chapter komik favorit lebih cepat dari yang lain, dan berbagai fitur lainnya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"77f464bd-adf7-533b-8589-974e2c16d0e1"}}}